.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Manages warning messages within a node\&. 

The \fBWarnings\fP class provides mechanisms to set, unset, and retrieve warning messages\&. It updates the GUI when warnings are changed\&.

.PP
This class is designed to be non-copyable to ensure warnings are managed centrally\&. 
